# Cursor Screenshot Server Rules

## Project
- MCP server for Cursor IDE screenshots
- Uses Puppeteer & Chrome
- Node.js/TypeScript
- Auto clipboard + paste integration
- Auto Ctrl+V/Cmd+V simulation

## Dependencies
- puppeteer
- chrome-launcher
- sharp
- img-clipboard
- @nut-tree-fork/nut-js
- @modelcontextprotocol/sdk

## Code Style
- TypeScript with strict typing
- ES modules (type: module)
- Functional over OOP
- Error handling with try/finally
- Async/await patterns

## Testing
- Manual testing only
- Use test/manual-screenshot.ts

## Build
- npm run build
- npm run watch (development)
- npm run inspector (testing) 